{
  "texts": [
    "The objective is to analyze the implementation of RPA within the banking sector.",
    "Netherlands ING Bank 2016 ING Bank of the Netherlands recently unveiled its strategic initiative, known as the RPA system, with the aim of preserving its staff via the establishment of a digital banking platform.",
    "KoreaShinhan Bank 2018 The RPA system was implemented by Shinhan Bank, including a total of 44 subprojects and involving 21 different departments.",
    "The RPA system effectively manages a daily workload of over 6000 processes for Shinhan Bank.",
    "China Bank of Nanjing 2018 A collaborative effort with Alibaba cloud resulted in the successful implementation of over 30 RPA applications."
  ]
}